api_list.name: Huuto.net and tori.fi query
api_list.description: Huuto.net and tori.fi query with chosen searchterm
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://huuto-net-tori-fi-item-finder.p.rapidapi.com/kaikki/auto"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "huuto-net-tori-fi-item-finder.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
